7 And ic me wende to ðære sæ allre witena;
8 cwæð: "Hwat secgð ðeos? and hwat andwyrdeð
9 ðæt oder fyr? and hwa sind ða ðe hit fremedon?"

25 Min heretoga eode niðer on ðone bat,
26 and syððan dyde me stigan æfter him;
27 and ða ða ic wæs ðærinne ða ðuhte he hefig.

34 And ic to him: "Gif ic cume, ne wunige ic;
35 ac ðu hwæt eart ðu, ðe ðus eart geworden atol?".
36 He andswarode: "Gesyh ðæt ic eom an ðe wepeð".

37 And ic him ða: "Mid weope and mid heofunge,
38 ðu werga gast, ðu wuna herinne;
39 forðam ic ðe cann, ðeah ðu sie eal besmiten."

40 Þa he ða handa tu on ðæt treowe strahte;
41 forðæm se wisa ðone wer sprengde,
42 cwæð: "Far nu ðær mid ðinum geferum!"

43 Þa he me mid his earmum beclypte;
44 he me cyste on wlite and cwæð: "Sawl unrot,
45 gebletsod seo ðe on ðinum life gewrað!

46 He wæs on worulde wlitig man;
47 nis nan fromnes ðe his gemynd wlite:
48 forðæm is his sceadu her swa swiðe yrre.

61 Ealle grymetedon: "To Filippe Argenti!";
62 and se Florentinisca gast unbliðe
63 on him sylfum wende mid his toðum.

64 Þær we hine læfdon, and na mare ne secge;
65 ac on ðam eare me wearð dolg geslagen,
66 þurh ðone ic ða eagan on ða gesyhðe sceawode.

100 ne læt ðu me," cwæð ic, "ðus gedrecedne;
101 and gif ðæt furðor ne mæg,
102 ðonne fundige we eft ðara forma."

112 Ne mihte ic gehyran ðæt he him to sæde;
113 ac ic ne wæs ðær mid him lange,
114 forðæm ðe ælc innon ða urnon, ða ðe oðre.

124 Þeos ofermod nis nawiht niwe;
125 forðæmðehiehitæræthæfdonætmærregeate,
126 ðeungelocenisgytisfynd.
